0.1.3.1	fix some tiny bugs
	* do not segfault on file without extension
	* allow the use of extension of any case type

0.1.3	add more command line option
	* -v, -vv: to change verbosity of output
	* -f: to force overwrite of existing files
	* -s: to disable the addition of a comment field in the hidim (png)

0.1.2 	bug fix: encode function
	for some data and some value of line length, hidim produced was incorrect

0.1.1	use getopt to parse command-line option
	* to change line length of hidim
	* to remove border and hidim logo

0.1	initial release
